<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2134/95 of 7 September 1995 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2814/90 and laying down certain detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 as regards the transfer of premium rights between members of the same producer groups and increasing the premium rights of certain sheepmeat and goatmeat producers in Italy and Greece </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2134/95, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2814/90 ja kehtestatakse teatavad n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguste &uuml;leandmise kohta samade tootjar&uuml;hmade liikmete vahel ning suurendatakse teatavate Itaalia ja Kreeka lamba- ja kitselihatootjate lisatasu saamise &otilde;igusi 7. september 1995 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 of 25 September 1989 on the common organization of the market in sheepmeat and goatmeat (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1265/95 (2), and in particular Article 5 (1) and (9) and Article 5a (4) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. septembri 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 lamba- ja kitselihaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1265/95, (2) eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;ikeid 1 ja 9 ning artikli 5a l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89 of 12 December 1989 defining lambs fattened as heavy carcases (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1266/95 (4), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 12. detsembri 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89, millega m&auml;&auml;ratletakse rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatud talled, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1266/95, (4) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the last subparagraph of Article 5a (4) (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 stipulates that the provision whereby, in the case of a transfer of premium rights without transfer of the holding, a part of the premium rights is to be surrendered without compensation to the national reserve does not apply to members of the same producer groups meeting certain conditions to be determined by the Commission in accordance with the procedure provided for in Article 30; whereas, in order to prevent irregularities, minimum conditions should consequently be laid down, the Member States being authorized, where applicable, to lay down additional conditions; whereas the penalties applying where such conditions are not met should also be specified; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5a l&otilde;ike 4 punkti b viimases l&otilde;igus s&auml;testatakse, et s&auml;tet, mille alusel lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguste &uuml;leandmise korral ilma talumajapidamise &uuml;leandmiseta tuleb osa lisatasu saamise &otilde;igusi loovutada riigi varudesse h&uuml;vitiseta, ei kohaldata sama tootjar&uuml;hma liikmete suhtes, kes j&auml;rgivad teatavaid tingimusi, mille komisjon m&auml;&auml;rab artiklis 30 s&auml;testatud korras; seet&otilde;ttu tuleks eeskirjade eiramise v&auml;ltimiseks s&auml;testada teatavad miinimumtingimused, lubades liikmesriikidel vajaduse korral s&auml;testada t&auml;iendavaid tingimusi; samuti tuleks t&auml;psustada karistused, mida kohaldatakse juhul, kui neid tingimusi ei t&auml;ideta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the third and following subparagraphs of Article 5b (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 provide for the establishment of special reserves with a ceiling of 600 000 rights for both Italy and Greece to permit them to grant additional rights to certain producers; whereas that Regulation lays down criteria for identifying such producers and for determining their additional rights and provides for a verification procedure by the Commission; whereas to that end provision should be made for a single centralized register to be kept by each Member State so that the producers concerned can be located and all the details needed for such verification are available; whereas, in addition, the penultimate subparagraph of the abovementioned Article 5b (1) provides that such verification must ensure that the additional rights will be allocated in such a way that such producers do not ultimately obtain more rights than would have been granted them had the situation which led to the creation of additional rights not occurred; whereas to that end provision should be made for the contribution referred to in the first subparagraph of abovementioned Article 5b (1) not to be included in the national reserve so that producers other than those referred to above may not benefit under the measure provided for in this Regulation; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5b l&otilde;ike 1 kolmandas l&otilde;ikes ja j&auml;rgmistes l&otilde;igetes s&auml;testatakse erivarude kehtestamine, mille &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r on 600 000 &otilde;igust nii Itaalias kui ka Kreekas, v&otilde;imaldamaks neil anda teatavatele tootjatele t&auml;iendavaid &otilde;igusi; selles m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatakse kriteeriumid selliste tootjate kindlakstegemiseks ja nende t&auml;iendavate &otilde;iguste m&auml;&auml;ratlemiseks ning n&auml;hakse ette komisjoni kontrollimenetlus; sel eesm&auml;rgil tuleks s&auml;testada igas liikmesriigis &uuml;he tsentraliseeritud registri pidamine, mis v&otilde;imaldab asjaomaste tootjate leidmise ja k&otilde;igi selliseks kontrollimiseks vajalike &uuml;ksikasjade k&auml;ttesaadavuse; lisaks sellele s&auml;testatakse eespool nimetatud artikli 5b l&otilde;ike 1 eelviimases l&otilde;igus, et selline kontrollimine peab tagama t&auml;iendavate &otilde;iguste jaotamise viisil, mis ei anna sellistele tootjatele l&otilde;ppkokkuv&otilde;ttes rohkem &otilde;igusi, kui neile oleks antud juhul, kui t&auml;iendavate &otilde;iguste kehtestamise p&otilde;hjustanud olukorda poleks tekkinud; sel eesm&auml;rgil tuleks s&auml;testada, et eespool nimetatud artikli 5b l&otilde;ike 1 esimeses l&otilde;igus nimetatud osamaksu ei h&otilde;lmata riigi varudega, et muud tootjad peale eespool nimetatute ei saaks k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses etten&auml;htud meedet kasutada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the newly created additional rights constitute compensation by virtue of the fact that in Italy and Greece, 1991, which was the reference marketing year for determining rights, coincided with the switchover between two different premium systems resulting in under-estimation of rights; whereas the producers receiving such additional rights should not therefore be penalized by applying to them the condition laid down in Article 6 (1) of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3567/92 (5), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1847/95 (6); </inglise>
<eesti> uued t&auml;iendavad &otilde;igused kujutavad endast h&uuml;vitust seet&otilde;ttu, et Itaalias ja Kreekas langes 1991. v&otilde;rdlusmajandusaasta &otilde;iguste m&auml;&auml;ramiseks kokku &uuml;leminekuga &uuml;helt lisatasu s&uuml;steemilt teisele, mille tagaj&auml;rjel &otilde;igusi alahinnati; selliseid t&auml;iendavaid &otilde;igusi saavaid tootjaid ei tohiks seet&otilde;ttu karistada, kohaldades nende suhtes komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3567/92, (5) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1847/95, (6) artikli 6 l&otilde;ikes 1 etten&auml;htud tingimust; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the second subparagraph of Article 1 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89 provides for the introduction of a simplified procedure for verification of fattening as heavy carcases with regard to lambs belonging to a limited number of meat breeds reared in geographically well-defined areas; whereas to that end Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2814/90 of 28 September 1990 laying down detailed rules for the definition of lambs fattened as heavy carcases (7), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 277/94 (8), should be amended to simplify the administrative verification procedure laid down while maintaining the obligation on producers to show they have actually fattened as heavy carcases all lambs born on their holdings; whereas that obligation may be deemed to have been fulfilled where a check shows that the lambs present as a percentage of the ewes is above a minimum threshold determined by reference to normal breeding practice for the breeds and areas concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 teises l&otilde;igus s&auml;testatakse lihtsustatud korra kehtestamine geograafiliselt selgepiirilistel aladel kasvatatud piiratud arvu lihat&otilde;ugudesse kuuluvate lammaste rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumamise kontrollimiseks; sel eesm&auml;rgil tuleks muuta komisjoni 28. septembri 1990. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2814/90, millega kehtestatakse rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatud tallede m&auml;&auml;ratlemise &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad, (7) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 277/94, (8) et lihtsustada etten&auml;htud halduskontrolli korda, s&auml;ilitades tootjate kohustuse n&auml;idata, et nad on tegelikult k&otilde;ik oma talumajapidamistes s&uuml;ndinud talled rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumanud; selle kohustuse v&otilde;ib lugeda t&auml;idetuks, kui kontrollimine n&auml;itab, et olemasolevate tallede protsent uttede hulgas on suurem alamm&auml;&auml;rast, mis m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks asjakohaste t&otilde;ugude ja piirkondade harilike t&otilde;uaretustavade alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Sheepmeat and Goatmeat, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las lamba- ja kitselihaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> To be eligible under the fourth subparagraph of Article 5a (4) (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89, members concerned of the same producer group must meet the following conditions: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5a l&otilde;ike 4 punkti b neljanda l&otilde;igu n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmiseks peavad asjaomased sama tootjar&uuml;hma liikmed j&auml;rgima j&auml;rgmisi tingimusi: </eesti>
<inglise> - they must continue to be members of the group for at least the three marketing years following that in respect of which the transfer of rights is notified by the producer surrendering his rights; </inglise>
<eesti> - nad peavad j&auml;tkuvalt olema r&uuml;hma liikmed v&auml;hemalt kolm majandusaastat p&auml;rast aastat, mille osas &otilde;igustest loobuv tootja teatab &otilde;iguste &uuml;leandmisest; </eesti>
<inglise> - they must have the status of producers as defined in Article 1 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 3493/90 (1) and fulfil the obligations laid down in Article 2 of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2385/91 (2) throughout the abovementioned period. </inglise>
<eesti> - neil peab eespool nimetatud ajavahemiku v&auml;ltel olema n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3493/90 (9) artiklis 1 m&auml;&auml;ratletud tootja staatus ja nad peavad t&auml;itma komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2385/91 (10) artiklis 2 s&auml;testatud kohustusi. </eesti>
<inglise> However, the above conditions shall not apply where, during the said period, the producer concerned transfers to another member of the group his remaining rights with his holding. </inglise>
<eesti> Eespool nimetatud tingimusi ei kohaldata juhul, kui asjaomane tootja annab nimetatud ajavahemiku jooksul oma j&auml;relej&auml;&auml;nud &otilde;igused koos oma talumajapidamisega &uuml;le r&uuml;hma teisele liikmele. </eesti>
<inglise> Furthermore, the Member States shall lay down additional conditions where necessary to avoid jeopardizing the application of the third subparagraph of Article 5a (4) (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89; they shall inform the Commission thereof. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisaks sellele s&auml;testavad liikmesriigid vajaduse korral t&auml;iendavad tingimused, et v&auml;ltida m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5a l&otilde;ike 4 punkti b kolmanda l&otilde;igu kohaldamise ohustamist; nad teatavad sellest komisjonile. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Where, during the period referred to in paragraph 1, it is observed that at least one of the conditions laid down therein is not fulfilled, the third subparagraph of Article 5a (4) (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 shall apply as from the marketing year during which failure to fulfil the condition(s) is observed; in such cases, the Member States shall immediately recover the corresponding rights. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud ajavahemiku jooksul m&auml;rgatakse, et v&auml;hemalt &uuml;ht selles s&auml;testatud tingimustest ei t&auml;ideta, kohaldatakse m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5a l&otilde;ike 4 punkti b kolmandat l&otilde;iku alates majandusaastast, mille jooksul m&auml;rgati tingimus(t) e t&auml;itmataj&auml;tmist; sellistel juhtudel v&otilde;tavad liikmesriigid vastavad &otilde;igused viivitamatult tagasi. </eesti>
<inglise> This measure shall apply without prejudice to additional penalties laid down nationally. </inglise>
<eesti> Selle meetme kohaldamine ei piira t&auml;iendavate siseriiklikult etten&auml;htud karistuste kohaldamist. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> By 30 April each marketing year, the Member States shall notify the Commission of the number of producers and of animals falling within the scope of paragraph 1 during the preceding marketing year and, where applicable, the penalties as referred to in paragraph 2 and the number of rights recovered where such penalties are applied. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga majandusaasta 30. aprilliks teatavad liikmesriigid komisjonile eelmisel majandusaastal l&otilde;ike 1 reguleerimisalaga h&otilde;lmatud tootjate ja loomade arvu ning vajaduse korral l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud karistused ja tagasiv&otilde;etud &otilde;iguste arvu, kui selliseid karistusi kohaldatakse. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The areas of Italy referred to in the second indent of Article 5b (1) (a) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 shall be as listed in the Annex. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5b l&otilde;ike 1 punkti a teises taandes osutatud Itaalia piirkonnad on loetletud lisas. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The national reserve shall not receive the percentage provided for in the first subparagraph of Article 5b (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 following the allocation of the additional rights provided for in the third subparagraph of that paragraph. </inglise>
<eesti> Riigi varud ei saa m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5b l&otilde;ike 1 esimeses l&otilde;igus s&auml;testatud protsenti p&auml;rast selle l&otilde;ike kolmandas alal&otilde;igus etten&auml;htud t&auml;iendavate &otilde;iguste jaotamist. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Before the end of the 1995 marketing year, Italy and Greece shall complete the administrative procedure for identifying the producers referred to in the third and following subparagraphs of Article 5b (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89. </inglise>
<eesti> Enne 1995. majandusaasta l&otilde;ppu l&otilde;petavad Itaalia ja Kreeka haldusprotseduuri m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5b l&otilde;ike 1 kolmandas l&otilde;igus ja j&auml;rgmistes l&otilde;ikudes nimetatud tootjate kindlakstegemiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> To that end, those Member States shall in particular each keep a single centralized register enabling the producers concerned to be located by administrative unit; the registers shall in particular show in respect of each producer: </inglise>
<eesti> Sel eesm&auml;rgil peavad k&otilde;nealused liikmesriigid eelk&otilde;ige &uuml;ht tsentraliseeritud registrit, mis v&otilde;imaldab asjaomaste tootjate leidmist haldus&uuml;ksuste kaupa; registrid n&auml;itavad iga tootja kohta eelk&otilde;ige j&auml;rgmist: </eesti>
<inglise> - the producer's name and address, </inglise>
<eesti> - tootja nimi ja aadress, </eesti>
<inglise> - the number of premium rights originally granted, </inglise>
<eesti> - esialgselt antud lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguste arv, </eesti>
<inglise> - the number of premium rights already granted from the national reserve, the conditions applying and the increase provided for under this Regulation, </inglise>
<eesti> - juba riigi varudest antud lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguste arv, kohaldatavad tingimused ja k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses etten&auml;htud suurendamine, </eesti>
<inglise> - the number of premiums already granted for the 1991 and 1992 marketing years, </inglise>
<eesti> - juba 1991. ja 1992. majandusaasta eest antud lisatasude arv, </eesti>
<inglise> - the producer's category in accordance with the abovementioned subparagraphs under (a) first and second indent and under (b) first and second indent. </inglise>
<eesti> - tootja kategooria vastavalt eespool nimetatud l&otilde;ikudele punkti a esimeses ja teises taandes ning punkti b esimeses ja teises taandes. </eesti>
<inglise> As soon as this identification procedure has been completed, Italy and Greece shall so inform the Commission; the latter shall carry out the requisite verifications and shall notify the two Member States concerned of the number of additional rights that have been newly created. </inglise>
<eesti> Itaalia ja Kreeka teatavad kindlakstegemise korra l&otilde;petamisest viivitamata komisjonile; komisjon teostab vajaliku kontrolli ja teatab kahele asjaomasele liikmesriigile uute t&auml;iendavate &otilde;iguste arvu. </eesti>
<inglise> On the basis of such notification, Italy and Greece shall be authorized to pay out the advances on and the balance of the premiums corresponding to such additional rights as fixed for the 1995 marketing year; they shall inform the Commission thereof. </inglise>
<eesti> Sellise teate alusel on Itaalial ja Kreekal lubatud maksta ettemakseid ja lisatasude j&auml;&auml;ksummat, mis vastavad 1995. majandusaastaks kinnitatud t&auml;iendavatele &otilde;igustele; nad teatavad sellest komisjonile. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> Notwithstanding Article 6 (1) and Article 7 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 3567/92, producers who have obtained additional rights under this Regulation shall be authorized to transfer such rights and/or lease them temporarily. </inglise>
<eesti> Olenemata m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3567/92 artikli 6 l&otilde;ikest 1 ja artikli 7 l&otilde;ikest 2, v&otilde;ivad vastavalt k&auml;esolevale m&auml;&auml;rusele t&auml;iendavad &otilde;igused saanud tootjad neid &otilde;igusi &uuml;le anda ja/v&otilde;i neid ajutiselt loovutada. </eesti>
<inglise> Those paragraphs shall, however, continue to apply to rights held before such additional rights were obtained. </inglise>
