<inglise> 'Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> "Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Producers marketing sheep's milk or sheep's milk products who wish to benefit under the derogation provided for in the second subparagraph of Article 1 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89 with regard to lambs in the geographical areas and belonging to the breeds listed in the Annex hereto shall provide the following details in their premium applications, which must be submitted in the course of a set period between 1 November and 31 December preceding the beginning of the marketing year to which the premium relates: </inglise>
<eesti> Lambapiima v&otilde;i lambapiimatooteid turustavad tootjad, kes soovivad kasutada m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 teises l&otilde;igus selle m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas loetletud geograafiliste piirkondade ja seal nimetatud t&otilde;ugudesse kuuluvate tallede jaoks etten&auml;htud erandit, esitavad j&auml;rgmised &uuml;ksikasjad oma lisatasutaotlustes, mis tuleb esitada kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud ajavahemikul 1. novembrist 31. detsembrini enne majandusaastat, mille eest lisatasu antakse: </eesti>
<inglise> - the actual or expected lambing periods when the lambs to be fattened as heavy carcases during the marketing year are born; if the actual lambing periods subsequently turn out to be significantly different from those expected as referred to above, the producer shall so notify the competent authoritiy in writing within one month of the change, </inglise>
<eesti> - tegelikud v&otilde;i eeldatavad poegimisperioodid, mil s&uuml;nnivad sellel majandusaastal rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatavad talled; kui tegelikud poegimisperioodid osutuvad hiljem eespool nimetatud eeldatavatest perioodidest m&auml;rkimisv&auml;&auml;rselt erinevaks, teatab tootja sellest kirjalikult p&auml;devale asutusele kuu aja jooksul p&auml;rast muudatust, </eesti>
<inglise> - the number of lambs expected to be born during each period as referred to above as a percentage of total lambs born during the marketing year, </inglise>
<eesti> - igal eespool nimetatud perioodil eeldatavasti s&uuml;ndivate tallede arv protsendina majandusaasta jooksul s&uuml;ndivate tallede koguarvust, </eesti>
<inglise> - an undertaking to rear on the holding all lambs born to ewes declared in the premium application and to fatten them as heavy carcases. </inglise>
<eesti> - kohustus kasvatada talumajapidamises k&otilde;ik lisatasutaotluses deklareeritud uttedele s&uuml;ndinud talled ja nuumata nad rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks. </eesti>
<inglise> Notwithstanding the first subparagraph of Article 1 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89, lambs present with the ewes at the time of the inspection shall be considered to be fattened as heavy carcases, the inspection being carried out during a period which allows the lambs to fulfil the conditions on fattening laid down in paragraph 1 (c) of that Article. </inglise>
<eesti> Olenemata m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 esimesest l&otilde;igust loetakse kontrollimise ajal uttede juures olevad talled rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatavateks, kui kontroll toimub ajavahemikul, mille t&otilde;ttu on v&otilde;imalik, et talled vastavad selle artikli l&otilde;ike 1 punktis c etten&auml;htud nuumamistingimustele. </eesti>
