<inglise> Producers complying with the obligations set out in paragraph 1 shall receive the premium for the heavy category referred to in Article 5 (4) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 in respect of all their eligible ewes; to that end the undertaking to rear on their holdings all lambs born to ewes declared shall be considered to have been fulfilled if, at the time of the inspection, except in duly justified exceptional circumstances, the number of lambs present as a percentage of ewes which have lambed during the lambing period covering the lambs subject to the inspection is at least 70 %; otherwise, the premium for the light category shall be paid for the eligible ewes provided that, in the view of the competent authority, the difference is not due to a false declaration made deliberately or through serious negligence. </inglise>
<eesti> L&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud tingimusi t&auml;itvad tootjad saavad k&otilde;igi oma k&otilde;lblike uttede eest m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud raske kategooria lisatasu; sel eesm&auml;rgil loetakse t&auml;idetuks kohustus kasvatada talumajapidamises k&otilde;ik deklareeritud uttedele s&uuml;ndinud talled, kui kontrollimise ajal, v&auml;lja arvatud &otilde;igustatud erandlikel asjaoludel, on olemasolevate tallede arv v&auml;hemalt 70% uttede arvust, kes on poeginud kontrolliga h&otilde;lmatud tallede poegimisperioodil; muudel juhtudel makstakse lisatasuk&otilde;lblike uttede eest kerge kategooria lisatasu tingimusel, et p&auml;deva asutuse arvates ei ole erinevus tingitud tahtlikult v&otilde;i t&otilde;sise hooletuse t&otilde;ttu esitatud valeandmetest. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the competent authority finds that the information contained in a premium application pursuant to paragraph 1 constitutes a false declaration made deliberately or through serious negligence, the producer concerned shall also loss the right to the premium in accordance with Article 5 (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 for the marketing year in respect of which the false declaration is found to have been made. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui p&auml;dev asutus leiab, et lisatasutaotluses sisalduv, l&otilde;ikele 1 vastav teave kujutab endast tahtlikult v&otilde;i t&otilde;sise hooletuse t&otilde;ttu esitatud valeandmeid, kaotab asjaomane tootja vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikele 3 &otilde;iguse lisatasule majandusaasta eest, mille osas on valeandmeid esitatud." </eesti>
